ds.util
Class HashSet<T>

java.lang.Object
  ds.util.HashSet<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection<T>, Set<T>, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<T>
public class HashSet<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Set<T>, java.lang.Cloneable, Iterable<T>

This class implements the Set interface, backed by a hash table (actually a HashMap instance). It makes no guarantees as to the iteration order of the set.

See Also:
HashMap
